# =============================================================================
# Team Definitions (for reference)
# =============================================================================

# Core Teams:
# @architecture-team - System architecture and design decisions
# @backend-team - Python services and API development
# @frontend-team - React UI and user experience
# @devops-team - Infrastructure, deployment, and CI/CD
# @qa-team - Quality assurance and testing
# @ai-team - AI/ML systems and agent development

# Specialized Teams:
# @security-team - Security and compliance
# @performance-team - Performance optimization
# @documentation-team - Technical documentation
# @product-team - Product requirements and features
# @release-team - Release management and deployment
# @data-team - Data processing and analytics

# Domain Expert Teams:
# @server-team - Archon server specialists
# @mcp-team - Model Context Protocol experts
# @agents-team - AI agents and orchestration
# @ui-ux-team - User interface and experience design
# @database-team - Database and schema management
# @api-team - API design and integration
